==學術及政策相關使用==
{{distinguish|種族滅絕|文化灭绝}}
[[File:Bouddhas_de_Bâmiyân_-_Aout_2005.jpg|right]]：[[塔利班|塔利班]]藉口以[[伊斯蘭|伊斯蘭]]教義破壞[[巴米揚大佛|巴米揚大佛]]的行為，被世界各地的伊斯蘭領袖稱為是對人類做出此「[[文化灭绝|文化灭绝]]」的破壞行為，而非侷限於特定种族<ref name="Kornblum2011">{{cite book|author=William Kornblum|title=Sociology in a Changing World|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=DtKcG6qoY5AC&pg=PT429|accessdate=2013-02-26|date=2011-01-31|publisher=Cengage Learning|isbn=978-1-111-30157-6|pages=429|quote=This Afghan statue of the Buddha, carved into a mountainside over 1,500 years ago, was destroyed by the Taliban, the intensely fundamental Islamic government that was deposed in 2001 by a United Nations-sanctioned invasion. The Taliban ruled Afghanistan according to its own interpretations of Islamic and tribal Pashtun laws. Islamic leaders throughout the world condemned the destruction as "un-Islanic" and "an act of cultural genocide against humanity."|archive-date=2015-03-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150321195756/http://books.google.com/books?id=DtKcG6qoY5AC&pg=PT429|dead-url=no}}</ref>。]]
;使用及誤用
有時「种族文化灭绝」一詞用來取代「[[文化灭绝|文化灭绝]]」，然而這用法混淆了[[族群|族群]]（{{lang-en|ethnicity}}）與[[文化|文化]]的不同概念<ref name="DelantyKumar2006"/>。舉例來說，[[塔利班|塔利班]]藉口以[[伊斯蘭|伊斯蘭]]教義破壞[[巴米揚大佛|巴米揚大佛]]的行為，被世界各地的伊斯蘭領袖稱為是對人類做出此「文化灭绝」的破壞行為，而非侷限於特定种族<ref name="Kornblum2011"/>。

回顧法律和學術史的關於[[種族滅絕|種族滅絕]]及种族文化灭绝兩詞使用差異：「種族滅絕」殺死人，而「種族文化滅絕」殺害的人的靈魂及造成社會文化之滅絕。<ref name="Clavero2008">{{cite book|author=Bartolomé Clavero|title=Genocide Or Ethnocide, 1933-2007: How to Make, Unmake, and Remake Law with Words|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=f_-_0d8JMtEC&pg=PA100|accessdate=2013-02-28|year=2008|publisher=Giuffrè Editore|isbn=978-88-14-14277-2|pages=100|quote=Genocide kills people while ethnocide kills social cultures through the killing of individual souls.|archive-date=2014-06-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140630195703/http://books.google.com/books?id=f_-_0d8JMtEC&pg=PA100|dead-url=no}}</ref>
此外，由於「文化滅絕」只能用來描述是種族滅絕的文化面向，然而「種族文化滅絕」的概念是不僅僅是「文化」上的滅絕，更包括較廣泛的「種族滅絕」的其他過程<ref name="Shaw2007">{{cite book|author=Martin Shaw|title=What is Genocide|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=sVnl-HgG4QEC&pg=PA65|accessdate=2013-02-28|date=2007-03-20|publisher=Polity|isbn=978-0-7456-3182-0|pages=65-67|quote=So the idea of ethnocide as 'cultural genocide' distinct from physically violent genocide is misleading, since cultural genocide can only be the cultural dimension ''of'' genocide, something which is integral to every genocidal attack. ... It is better to refer to cultural suppression for pre-genocidal denial of culture, the cultural dimension of genocide for suppression that is part of broader genocidal process, and unintentional group destruction for cases where groups are destroyed by disease and famine that are originally unintended.}}</ref>。

由於「种族文化灭绝」和[[文化滅絕|文化滅絕]]的概念在不同學術及法律等脈絡下有採用及停止採用的變化，研究「種族滅絕」的人類學研究亦將此納入和排除的相關法律和政策過程進行研究
<ref name="BloxhamMoses2010">{{cite book|author1=Donald Bloxham|author2=A. Dirk Moses|title=The Oxford Handbook of Genocide Studies|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=xCHMFHQRNtYC&pg=PR2-IA92|accessdate=2013-02-28|date=2010-04-15|publisher=Oxford University Press|isbn=978-0-19-161361-6|pages=2–|archive-date=2014-06-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140630192728/http://books.google.com/books?id=xCHMFHQRNtYC&pg=PR2-IA92|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

;人類學定義及討論

人類學的定義為：「暴力地消滅一個族群作為獨特群體的集體文化認同；發生在一個佔主導地位的社會故意破壞另一個社會的文化遺產」；相關例子包括1950年代[[中國|中國]]的西藏政策、[[巴西|巴西]]1968年時對[[亞馬遜河流域|亞馬遜河流域]]印地安原住民的暴力對待、等等<ref name="HavilandPrins2010"/>。

